data.description: This beautifully renovated 3-bedroom home is the perfect start for a first time homebuyer. Nestled in a tranquil cul-de-sac, this home strikes the perfect balance between serene suburban living and convenient access to the city. Step inside to find a spacious and inviting living area, perfect for entertaining or relaxing with family, an eat-in kitchen with ample amount of cabinet space and a separate dining room to host holiday and special dinners.  Upstairs, the primary suite is a true retreat, boasting a custom entertainment built-in and reading nook and generously sized secondary bedrooms. Lastly, step out to the spacious private backyard that has the potential to create the perfect future oasis.
